  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::AbstractOcclusion.WebGpuWater.Demo.DemoOverlay
  title: Reflexion trio
  description: 'Demonstrate the different reflection type . Planar : add planar reflection
    script to camera , remove water from reflected layer , and tick planar in water
    volume . SSR : cant reflect the skybox , need to be used with cube map in look
    tab .  URP probe : Cretae reflexion using reflexion probe in scene . Procedural
    sky : The defaut sky , you can replace it by any custom cube map in look tab
    . '
